body: We were editing stale constants; we know that the constants edited with the current commits are being used.
We're 2 for 2 in passed tests. Restarting on Travis (will update the numbers as they come).

I probably won't get a chance to clean up anything here until Tuesday.

I'd say @soltanmm - merge when you're happy.

Found more thread pools.
Made them smaller.
Three restarts later, all three were successful :) i'll keep on restarting. Travis is fast today, everybody's out for the long weekend!
